      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "FLOW\n1. Patient scans QR → texts Twilio SMS number (consent first).\n2. /api/sms → checkin-service. Enroll: match a fake FHIR patient, pull triage note.\n3. Mock CDS authors the cellulitis monitoring protocol ONCE (frozen, cached per visit).\n4. Each check-in: Claude interprets answers + drafts next question; guardrail applies the\n   frozen flag→tier map deterministically (model never lowers a tier, never holds the pager).\n5. If the model senses worsening → VIGIL CALLS the patient (ElevenLabs + Twilio Voice) —\n   unscripted; transcript returns into the same pipeline. [STRETCH / video-guaranteed]\n6. On Escalate → Notifier pages the nurse (SMS) + flags the EMR dashboard.\n7. Nurse EMR UI polls Supabase: dashboard + patient record + SBAR. Acknowledge → agent\n   goes silent (patient is not told; the nurse just goes to see them).\n\nREAL today: Twilio SMS · Claude · guardrail · Supabase · mock EMR UI · nurse page · SBAR.\nMOCKED: CDS (Glass Health), FHIR/EMR.   STRETCH: the ElevenLabs voice call.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FLOW\n1. Patient scans QR → texts Twilio SMS number (consent first).\n2. /api/sms → checkin-service. Enroll: match a fake FHIR patient, pull triage note.\n3. Mock CDS authors the cellulitis monitoring protocol ONCE (frozen, cached per visit).\n4. Each check-in: Claude interprets answers + drafts next question; guardrail applies the\n   frozen flag→tier map deterministically (model never lowers a tier, never holds the pager).\n5. If the model senses worsening → VIGIL CALLS the patient (ElevenLabs + Twilio Voice) —\n   unscripted; transcript returns into the same pipeline. [STRETCH / video-guaranteed]\n6. On Escalate → Notifier pages the nurse (SMS) + flags the EMR dashboard.\n7. Nurse EMR UI polls Supabase: dashboard + patient record + SBAR. Acknowledge → agent\n   goes silent (patient is not told; the nurse just goes to see them).\n\nREAL today: Twilio SMS · Claude · guardrail · Supabase · mock EMR UI · nurse page · SBAR.\nMOCKED: CDS (Glass Health), FHIR/EMR.   STRETCH: the ElevenLabs voice call.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 13.5
    }
